WWW/SpiTract version 0.01
=========================

WWW::SpiTract is a powerful tool for webpage retrieval plus a text analyzer.
Users can write a site description file, and WWW::SpiTract can fetch web pages and retrieve data automatically.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


